nodes.text: Nelsel was a Dathomirian Zabrak female from Dathomir who was the member of the Nightsisters, a group of witches, during the Clone Wars. When Arzo Suun, a former member of the warrior group, the Nightbrothers, hired fellow Nightbrothers Ruul and Mak Eak to steal from a warehouse-like building in the Nightbrother village, Nelsel and a couple Nightsisters caught the brothers after she sensed their presence in the Force.
